    "long_instructions": "## Ethics & Impact\r\n\r\nNow that you’ve developed a proposed solution, it's time to reflect on its **ethical implications** and **societal impact**.\r\n\r\nChat with the AI to:\r\n\r\n* Synthesize feedback from your peers and improve your solution.\r\n* Identify ethical concerns related to fairness, privacy, and sustainability.\r\n* Explore potential risks and unintended consequences of your innovation.\r\n* Develop strategies to address challenges and ensure your design is responsible.\r\n",
